---
By: Samuel Johnson
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 96
    Verse: 4
Tags:
  - Depression/Despair
---
When any fit of ... gloominess or perversion of the mind lays hold upon you,
make it a rule not to publish it by complaints but exert your whole care to
hide it. By endeavoring to hide it, you will drive it away.
